<%= @host.shortname  %>:
  keep: 1D
  type: remote
  user: backupninja
  home: "/var/backups/<%= @host.domain  %>/<%= @host.shortname  %>"
  host: haproxy.<%= @host.domain  %>

"/root/.ssh/id_rsa":
  ensure: file
  mode: '0600'
  content: <%= @host.params['id_dsa'] %>
"/root/.ssh/id_rsa.pub":
  ensure: file
  mode: '0644'
  content: <%= !@host.params['id_dsa.pub'].empty? && @host.params['id_dsa.pub'].split(@host.shortname + ": ").size > 1 ? @host.params['id_dsa.pub'].split(@host.shortname + ": ")[1].split("\n")[0] : "" %>
"/root/.ssh/known_hosts":
  ensure: file
  mode: '0644'
